OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,FOur reporter Lewis Andrews
OL,7,Finvestigates how rising funeral costs
OL,8,Fare straining grieving families.
OL,10,FA father and husband from Jersey says
OL,11,Fit has been a "nightmare" covering the
OL,12,Fcost of his wife's death.
OL,14,FLast year, Josh lost Leah - the mother
OL,15,Fof his three young children - to
OL,16,Fcancer when she was aged just 32.
OL,18,F"You don't expect to lose someone at
OL,19,Fthat age to pass away, so you don't
OL,20,Fput those kinds of plans in place,"
OL,21,FJosh explains.
