OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,FIn a particularly emotional moment,
OL,7,FJosh says: "She did everything for our
OL,8,Fchildren. The day of my wife's passing
OL,9,Fwas the hardest, so watching her pass
OL,10,Faway... also having to come home and
OL,11,Ftell three children that their mum's
OL,12,Fnot coming home."
OL,14,FThough government payments covered the
OL,15,Fmajority of the funeral bill, Josh
OL,16,Fstill has not been able to pay the
OL,17,Frest off.
