OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,FJosh explains: "There are moments
OL,7,Fwhere the children have gone to bed
OL,8,Fand I'm just sat on the sofa thinking
OL,9,Fabout what I need to pay and needs to
OL,10,Fbe paid.
OL,12,F"But then I just turn to the wife -
OL,13,Fobviously having her ashes at home - I
OL,14,Fspeak to her and say 'What do I pay
OL,15,Ffirst? What do I do?'"
OL,17,FA recent Freedom of Information
OL,18,Frequest revealed that the number of
OL,19,Fpeople claiming government help with
OL,20,Ffuneral costs has more than doubled
OL,21,Fsince 2014.
