OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,F"However, we're being charged more for
OL,7,Feverything: the crematorium or
OL,8,Fcemetery, churchyard, clergy,
OL,9,Forganists, service sheets, cost of
OL,10,Ffuel - everything goes up and we have
OL,11,Fto keep in line with that.
OL,13,F"From the time I started 35 years ago,
OL,14,Ffunerals were around #600. Now a full-
OL,15,Fon funeral is about #6,000."
