OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,FGovernment support comes as a lump sum
OL,7,F- called a death grant - for eligible
OL,8,Fislanders. Those on income support may
OL,9,Falso be able to get an extra payment
OL,10,Fwhich can cover the majority of the
OL,11,Fcost.
OL,13,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, Jersey's
OL,14,FSocial Security Minister, said: "We
OL,15,Fall know the cost of living is a huge
OL,16,Ffactor here on the island.
OL,18,F"I think the main thing for me is that
OL,19,Fthe people eligible for support do
OL,20,Fclaim it and don't worry about the
OL,21,Fneed to claim."
