OL,3,C'It's a nightmare': Grieving father
OL,4,Cshocked by increasing 'cost of dying'
OL,6,FJosh praised the support he received
OL,7,Ffrom funeral directors and Social
OL,8,FSecurity, and bereavement support
OL,9,Fcharities can also help.
OL,11,FHowever, Josh wants to raise more
OL,12,Fawareness of the financial impact a
OL,13,Ffamily death can have, saying people
OL,14,Fshould be more prepared than he was
OL,15,Ffor a complete change in his
OL,16,Fcircumstances during a cost-of-living
OL,17,Fcrisis.
